 present the spatially resolved kinematics and physical\nproperties of gas and stars, and depict the evolutionary history of this\ngalaxy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Apr 2017 18:40:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Apr 2017 12:36:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-26"}
