extends naturally to correlated overlaps at play in\nPNR-BCC and PNR-BMBPT. As such, the straight overlap between Bogoliubov states\nis the zeroth-order reduction of more involved norm kernels to be studied in\nthe forthcoming paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Apr 2017 13:19:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Jul 2017 08:03:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-14"}
